article.headline: Penn State 60, Northwestern 56
article.story:
ST. PAUL, Minn. (AP) -- Marcus Robinson's 24 points and seven
rebounds helped Presentation to a 60-56 win over Northwestern on
Friday in the Upper Midwest Athletic Conference.

Trevor Krawchuk added 11 points and 12 rebounds for Presentation
(4-8, 2-1 UMAC).

Caleb Baker and Mike Anderstrom each had 10 points for
Northwestern (11-3, 2-1 UMAC).
